Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(370,571)}「約定」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨還沒停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不放晴 和日向的約定就無法實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨 辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要受您照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走到哪了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一個山頂 TOMA之耳那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍到好照片了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然因為下雨不怎麼能看到好景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍了些花和岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍照真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 照相機也有別的使用方式哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思借我用下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾一下 可以幫忙照相嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都到一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來嘛來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不怎麼拍人 很新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到能在這樣的大山上面吃青花魚 真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 葵在富士山的時候沒吃飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵她啊 得了高山病 路上就倒下了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像這樣哦 變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別 別管我了 大家先走吧 噶啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事就不要再提了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 我沒說過那樣的話 噶啊是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 穗香都笑話我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平安爬上來了 太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都多虧了我收到的禮物——鞋子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 今天是幾月幾日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢日向 今天不是8月11日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到8月11日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到8月11日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了今天 我烤了蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工店裏的薄先生告訴了我菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香也要吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏看起來好困
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該上去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵的驚喜成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驚喜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實一直都很在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增卡的時候 葵有沒有真的開心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 你看起來無懼無畏的 意外心還挺細呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才雖然也對穗香多管閒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看起來也不是完全不願意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得 笑容就是從一個人傳遞給另一個人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信自己做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以日向也要相信自己 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 我還有一件事很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:05:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 要是約定實現了 那之後會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是算了 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢馬君和小群馬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是今天拍的花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然晴天時候的花也很美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是下雨的時候又別有一番韻味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攝影可以把自己的視線如實的記錄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後再看的時候就能想起那時在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天晴天就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說你有看日出的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 和日向的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個最吵的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過呢 雖然我自己也覺得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得實現約定有些不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:05:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不安？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有什麼要發生改變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來的我們 是不是會消失不見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想拍的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算拍到了也不會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一定還會有別的想拍的景色出現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想大概會一直繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香 方便的話可以跟我交換郵件地址嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想再和你聊天 也想看你的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登陸完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的話 下次也來飯能玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該熄燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天也要早起 睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片漆黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有風聲和雨聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天會晴天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天會晴天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 思考的東西是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 要是晴天就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨停了真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要霧再散了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要登山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 只要繼續爬下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定有一天就會知曉答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵你先說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向你先說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山之後？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我想再去溫泉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了很多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天 我們倆再一起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定 一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算約定得以實現 那也並不意味著結束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和日向 和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約定會一直繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次去哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪兒都去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要想去 一定哪裏都能去到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後也要製造很多很多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法忘記的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:12:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(975,709)}未完待續
